{"tid":384091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贊唔贊成立法，係公共車廂內大聲講野要罰錢","createTime":"2017-09-02T05:02:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T05:09:57.000Z","uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9788eb953075f640e6b0b1d74bd45759dfd98620","tid":384091,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:02:40.000Z","msg":"只要用手機拍低片段就可以交去地鐵舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753d94b1a11615a1ca2028c70c36cc4915781b7b","tid":384091,"uid":50565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只要用手機拍低片段就可以交去地鐵舉報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港真係好撚嘈，由其D細佬，個撚個係到叫但父母唔阻止又唔教真係好撚仆街。日本人由細到大都養成唔會成車廂內喧嘩，香港人真係出少句聲或者細聲D講嘢好似會死咁！"},{"pid":"2605ed0db160885ba231f9c1af16c401ed20df51","tid":384091,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"地鐵拍攝唔係犯法咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}